3. **Keep hand open while moving** → Draws continuous smooth line
4. **Close hand** → Stops drawing, clears the path
5. **Open hand elsewhere** → Starts fresh path at new location (no line connecting to old position)

This should eliminate the unwanted line that was connecting your previous drawing position to your new position when you reopened your hand!"}]},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"
